      <h2 class="section-title text-balance">China Green Card vs. Work Visa: Is the Upgrade Worth It?</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">Many long-term residents stay on annual temporary residence permits for years out of habit or uncertainty. Here is a direct comparison to help you decide.</p>

      <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
        <table class="compare-table" role="table" aria-label="Green card versus work visa comparison">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">Factor</th>
