      <h2 class="section-title text-balance">Limitations &amp; Responsibilities That Come with the Card</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">The China permanent residence card is not citizenship. Understanding its limits prevents legal surprises and helps you plan your life correctly.</p>

      <div class="limits-grid">
        <div class="limit-item">
          <div class="limit-icon stop" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7.5" stroke="#dc2626"></circle><path d="M5 8h6" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div>
